        "created_at": "2023-07-16T20:24:57.767Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I agree that the stale bot is a bit aggressive and somewhat annoying, but to be fair, it <em>does</em> ask for confirmation of whether the bug still exists and gives a grace period for someone to comment that, yes, this issue is still there, in which case it will reset the timer and leave the issue open. So if bugs are getting closed as stale, that means no one thought it was important enough to reply to stale bot and keep it open.</p>\n<p>I think they need to configure it so that they can tag an issue as ‚Äúacknowledged‚Äù or something and have stale bot ignore those, or at least give them a longer stale period, because it‚Äôs definitely too short as it is.</p>",
