        "created_at": "2023-07-20T12:54:27.286Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Hey,<br>\nthat sounds reasonable.</p>\n<p>Thing is‚Ä¶ I never noticed any grace period. So I guess it is very short. (I could not keep a bug going if it was below, say, two weeks. Since I only check such things once a week.)</p>\n<p>Anyway, in that case, nothing needs to be done. I will have to check if it really gave a grace period, and only report back if a bug got closed without any grace period or it is extremely short.</p>\n<p>Thank you for the reply. All conflicts are caused by miscommunication, and you resolved that. :)</p>",
